This is a Vite + React 18 project.
Language: plain JavaScript ES2022. NO TypeScript ever.
Styling: vanilla CSS only. NO Tailwind. NO inline styles. NO CSS modules.
Routing: react-router-dom v6. Use useNavigate not useHistory.
State: useState and useEffect only. No Redux, no Zustand, no Context unless asked.
API base: import.meta.env.VITE_API_URL — never hardcode URLs.
Auth: JWT in localStorage via src/lib/auth.js — use getToken() everywhere.
Components live in src/components/Name/Name.jsx with co-located Name.css.
Never install new npm packages without asking first.
Never use TypeScript syntax, type annotations, or .ts extensions.